title: Ace Video Workshop 1.6
description:
ce Video Workshop helps you join and convert avi files or mpeg files to a large VCD/DVD/SVCD compliant mpeg file for burning to VCD/DVD that can be played on VCD players and DVD players.

Here are some key features of ?Ace Video Workshop?:

? Convert avi to VCD/DVD/SVCD compliant mpeg files.

? Convert mpeg file to avi.

? Convert mpeg file to divx.

? Join avi or mpeg files to a larget mpeg file.

? Join avi or mpeg files to a larget avi file.

? Avi to divx(change codec of avi files).

? Change format of mpeg files (PAL<==>NTSC).

? Extract audio from video files .
